[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Disasters (settings)]]
Sets whether disasters off or on for a new map.<br><br>
0 = off - no disasters occur<br>
1 = on - disasters occur occasionally<br><br>
See [[en/Manual/Disasters]] for more information.

<pre>
[difficulty]
disasters = 0
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 ]

'''Default:''' 1


